## Approval Criteria

| Type | Criterion | PASS | FAIL |
|------|-----------|------|------|
| Visual | Console without errors | ✅ | ❌ |
| Visual | Content rendered | ✅ | ❌ Blank screen |
| Visual | Layout correct | ✅ | ❌ |
| Unit | All tests pass | ✅ | ❌ |
| Type | `bun run typecheck` passes | ✅ | ❌ |
